OL,3,CThe tax choice facing NI farmers
OL,5,FGetting your head around numbers can
OL,6,Fsometimes be a difficult task. Even
OL,7,Fmore so when it comes to taxes.
OL,9,FThat's exactly what Northern Ireland's
OL,10,Ffarming community has had to do
OL,11,Fthough, in just a few months.
OL,13,FAt the end of 2024, the Labour
OL,14,Fgovernment said it was going to remove
OL,15,Frelief on inheritance tax for farmers.
OL,17,FFrom April 2026, agricultural assets
OL,18,Fwhich total over #1m will be taxed at
OL,19,Fa rate of 20%.
