OL,3,CThe tax choice facing NI farmers
OL,5,FThat includes animals, buildings and
OL,6,Fland - with change now looming for
OL,7,Fmany farms in Northern Ireland.
OL,9,FFarms have been exempt from
OL,10,FAgricultural Property Relief and
OL,11,FBusiness Property Relief for many
OL,12,Fyears but that could now be changing.
OL,14,FIt was a decision not welcomed by many
OL,15,Ffarmers then, and even now, including
OL,16,Fdairy farmer Keith Agnew.
OL,18,FHe runs a large operation just outside
OL,19,Fof Newry, Co Down.
