OL,3,CThe tax choice facing NI farmers
OL,5,F"The simple fact is that the sector
OL,6,Fisn't profitable enough whenever you
OL,7,Fcount the valuation of property, to be
OL,8,Fable to sustain this for one
OL,9,Fgeneration, never mind two."
OL,11,FKeith spoke to UTV at Markethill
OL,12,FLivestock Sales in Co Armagh. Dairy
OL,13,Fand beef cattle were being sold on the
OL,14,Fday of filming and interest was still
OL,15,Fstrong, but under it all, lay concern
OL,16,Ffor what the future holds.
OL,18,FHampton Hewitt is the man behind the
OL,19,Fmicrophone and the man who coordinates
OL,20,Fthe sales.
