OL,5,FHis father John died in 2017, leaving
OL,6,Fthe family farm in Derrynoose to his
OL,7,Fmother Shirley before she passed it on
OL,8,Fto Timothy.
OL,10,F"Something so simple can absolutely
OL,11,Fobliterate farming," he told UTV.
OL,13,F"If they (the government) don't watch
OL,14,Fthemselves, they will do away with
OL,15,FIrish produce.
