OL,3,CThe tax choice facing NI farmers
OL,5,F"If inheritance tax hit me today, I
OL,6,Fwould have to sell a third of the
OL,7,Fplace and if I was to sell a third of
OL,8,Fthe place there wouldn't be enough
OL,9,Fincome to support me or if I was to
OL,10,Fhave a future family."
OL,12,FThe Ulster Farmers' Union is urging
OL,13,Fthe government to take on the concerns
OL,14,Fof farmers in Northern Ireland.
OL,16,F"It is gut-wrenching and really does
OL,17,Fpull on the heartstrings, some of the
OL,18,Fthings which farmers are actually
OL,19,Fconsidering," said James McCluggage
OL,20,Ffrom the union.
