OL,5,F"We need to see some sort of morality
OL,6,Fclause in there for the elderly, for
OL,7,Fthe disabled, for those who are
OL,8,Fincapacitated, that (sic) can't make a
OL,9,Fdecision or cannot get plans in place
OL,10,Fat the moment."
OL,12,FThe government says the changes won't
OL,13,Faffect every farmer and that they are
OL,14,Fnecessary to better fund public
OL,15,Fservices.
