OL,5,F"We are also slashing costs and red
OL,6,Ftape for food producers to export to
OL,7,Fthe EU, have appointed former NFU
OL,8,Fpresident Baroness Minette Batters to
OL,9,Frecommend reforms to boost farmers'
OL,10,Fprofits, and we're ensuring farmers
OL,11,Fget a bigger share of food contracts
OL,12,Facross our schools, hospitals, and
OL,13,Fprisons."
OL,15,FFor now, the industry looks determined
OL,16,Fto continue speaking up as farmers
OL,17,Fprepare to count the cost of change,
